---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import CrystalBall from "../assets/crystal-ball.svg";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy â€” Clairvoyance">
  <article class="privacy-page">
    <nav class="privacy-nav">
      <a href="/" class="brand-link">
        <CrystalBall width="20" height="20" />
        <span>Clairvoyance</span>
      </a>
    </nav>

    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: February 27, 2026</p>

    <h2>What Clairvoyance does</h2>
    <p>
      Clairvoyance is a set of software design skills for AI coding agents. All
      skills run locally inside your agent's session. Clairvoyance does not
      operate any servers, APIs, or external services.
    </p>

    <h2>Data collection</h2>
    <p>
      Clairvoyance does not collect, transmit, or store any user data. No
      telemetry, no analytics, no tracking. Your code never leaves your machine
      through Clairvoyance.
    </p>

    <h2>Third-party services</h2>
    <p>
      Clairvoyance has no MCP servers and no dependencies on external services.
      It consists of markdown skill files and prompt-based hooks that run
      entirely within your agent session.
    </p>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      This documentation site does not use cookies or any tracking technologies.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>
      If this policy changes, the update will be reflected here with a new date.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions? Open an issue on <a
        href="https://github.com/codybrom/clairvoyance">GitHub</a
      > or reach out to <a href="https://github.com/codybrom">Cody Bromley</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .privacy-page {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 3rem) 4rem;
    background: oklch(0.17 0.05 290);
    border-left: 1px solid oklch(1 0 0 / 0.03);
    border-right: 1px solid oklch(1 0 0 / 0.03);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .privacy-nav {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid oklch(1 0 0 / 0.06);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .brand-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: none;
    color: var(--text);
    transition: opacity 0.2s;

    & :global(svg) {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 12px oklch(0.75 0.12 75 / 0.3));
    }

    & span {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.7rem;
    }

    &:hover {
      opacity: 0.8;
    }
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 2.8rem);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .updated {
    font-family: var(--font-code);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  p {
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
</style>
